<page>
    <title>UWP web framework</title>
    <body>
        <![CDATA[
			<style>
				main section button[disabled]:after {
					content: ' (active)';
				}
			</style>

            <h2>UWP web framework</h2>

            <section>
                <h3>Hello!</h3>
                <p>Welcome to Universal Windows Platform web framework.</p>
                <p>Create web-based Universal Windows Platform applications in a blink of an eye! Use basic HTML syntax, and let UWP web framework do all the work for you!</p>

				<h3>4 beautiful, modern layouts</h3>
				<p>Check them out! Click one of the buttons below change the layout.</p>
				<button onClick="event.preventDefault(); Array.prototype.slice.call(document.querySelectorAll('main section button')).forEach(el => el.disabled = false); event.target.disabled = true; document.body.setAttribute('data-layouttype', 'tabs');">Tabs</button></li>
				<button href="#" onClick="event.preventDefault(); Array.prototype.slice.call(document.querySelectorAll('main section button')).forEach(el => el.disabled = false); event.target.disabled = true; document.body.setAttribute('data-layouttype', 'overlay');">Overlay</button></li>
				<button href="#" onClick="event.preventDefault(); Array.prototype.slice.call(document.querySelectorAll('main section button')).forEach(el => el.disabled = false); event.target.disabled = true; document.body.setAttribute('data-layouttype', 'docked-minimized');" disabled>Docked (minimized variant)</button></li>
				<button href="#" onClick="event.preventDefault(); Array.prototype.slice.call(document.querySelectorAll('main section button')).forEach(el => el.disabled = false); event.target.disabled = true; document.body.setAttribute('data-layouttype', 'docked');">Docked (always visible variant)</button></li>

                <h3>Get started</h3>
				<p>Check out the <a href="#" data-target="documentation" title="Documentation">documentation</a> to get help on your way to your first web-based Universal Windows Platform app.</p>
            </section>
        ]]>
    </body>
</page>